li.p:
We evaluate the expression in part (a) for t=38.         
		\begin{align*}
               4(t-20) \amp = 4(\alert{38}-20) \amp  \blert{\text{Simplify inside parentheses first.}}\\
                \amp = 4(18)=72                
                \end{align*}					
		The students paid $72 for the tickets.

